Yeah, but we had
to print these very small,

137
00:10:29,003 --> 00:10:33,298
and I wouldn't want you
to strain your eyes
twice in one day.

138
00:10:33,382 --> 00:10:35,717
Well, maybe you can
read it to me over lunch.

139
00:10:37,678 --> 00:10:40,805
Okay.
All right. I gotta stop by
the office first though.

140
00:10:40,890 --> 00:10:43,475
If I don't, the sheriffwill kill me.

141
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:46,519
They haven't had
a graduation dance since 1 945...

142
00:10:46,604 --> 00:10:48,605
