00:11:37,488 --> 00:11:39,406
I'm impressed.

158
00:11:39,490 --> 00:11:41,908
Thankyou.

159
00:11:41,992 --> 00:11:44,786
Check, please.

160
00:11:46,122 --> 00:11:49,499
