the graduation dance a little later.

163
00:11:58,134 --> 00:12:01,344
Well, maybe I can
come by for a while.

164
00:12:03,723 --> 00:12:05,682
Mark?

165
00:12:05,766 --> 00:12:08,393
Hmm?

