anything to worry about.

184
00:12:59,028 --> 00:13:02,447
Yeah, my deputy will let you know
if he sees anything.

185
00:13:02,531 --> 00:13:04,449
Mark.

186
00:13:04,533 --> 00:13:06,451
Oh, yeah. Mm-hmm.
[ Chuckles ]

187
00:13:06,535 --> 00:13:08,787
He's a good boy.

188
00:13:08,871 --> 00:13:10,830
