00:13:37,441 --> 00:13:39,150
Yes, sir.

199
00:13:39,235 --> 00:13:41,569
[ Laughs ]
You'll do fine.

200
00:13:41,654 --> 00:13:44,155
Come on down to Kingsley's
with me.

201
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:46,616
